question: List all known variants of the AGTR1 gene.
cypher:
MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('AGTR1')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('AGTR1'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50

MATCH (v:Variant)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(g:Gene)
WHERE toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('FRK')
   OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('FRK'))
RETURN v.name AS variant_name, g.symbol AS gene_symbol
LIMIT 50
